The autonomous bot system is now fully spec-compliant:

## Confluence Scoring (9 factors, max 10 pts)
1. Market Structure (2.0) — trend + CHoCH/BOS
2. Order Block (2.0) — price inside OB = full, nearby = 0.5
3. Fair Value Gap (1.5) — price inside FVG = full, nearby = 0.5
4. Premium/Discount (2.0) — buy in discount/sell in premium + OTE bonus
5. Kill Zone (1.0) — session kill zone active
6. Judas Swing (1.0) — confirmed = full, detected = 0.5
7. PD/PW Levels (0.5) — price within 0.2% of PDH/PDL/PWH/PWL
8. Reversal Candle (0.5) — pin bar or engulfing on latest bar
9. Liquidity Sweep (0.5) — pool with 2+ touches swept

## Safety Gates (10 gates)
1. HTF Bias (daily trend must agree)
2. Premium/Discount filter (only buy in discount, sell in premium)
3. Instrument enabled check
4. Max open positions (default 5)
5. Max per symbol (default 2)
6. Portfolio heat (default 10%)
7. Daily loss limit (default 5%)
8. Max drawdown (default 15%)
9. Min confluence score (default 6)
10. Min R:R ratio (default 1.5:1)

## Trade Reasoning
8-factor breakdown stored to trade_reasonings table on every trade.

## Post-Mortem
Auto-generated on close (SL/TP/manual/kill), stored to trade_post_mortems.
Includes: outcome, what worked, what failed, lesson learned.

## Config
Reads from bot_configs.config_json, falls back to defaults.
SL: structure-based with buffer. TP: 2R ratio. Risk: 1% per trade.
